"Application de gestion de contacto convergente per ambes scriptorio e "
"dispositivos mobile."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.phonebook.metainfo.xml:11
msgid ""
"It provides a central place for starting conversations. Depending on the "
"information available about a contact, respective actions are displayed."
msgstr ""
"Il forni un placia central per initiar conversationes. In dependentia del "
"information disponibile re un contacto, le respective actiones es monstrate."

